{"tid":1631840,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"態度好少少得唔得？控制下你地情緒","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:05.000Z","uid":243854,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d8666341bce3f79dd5d9abadcc61e25fb2060dda","tid":1631840,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"利申我係認同私了 但唔係亂私了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TkgwdWL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTkgwdWL.jpg&h=b9fd0843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0T6swJs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0T6swJs.jpg&h=d6798b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底係抄咗第一個POST定同一個人作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要肯定唔係警犬？點樣肯定到？<br />\n格式差唔多，手法一樣，又會咁清楚啲對白，講到喺隔離睇住但唔幫阻止下咁激動嘅手足？<br />\n<br />\n利申：支持等美國做嘢，和理非出場勇武暫時韜光養晦<br />\n不過唔覺得今日保護被恐怖分子撞擊嘅女手足有錯<br />\n幫黨企，黨鐵裝修亦都無錯(不過好似有人話觀塘站係警犬燒嘅？)"},{"pid":"955398daf93bc66bb157221e0ac98a0d409170f0","tid":1631840,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n你應承過會做勇武塊盾<br />\n宜家勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勿中林鄭割蓆計！</span></strong></span><br />\n記唔記得當初應承過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈都唔割</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣洗地</span></strong></span>開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d946e846465c57492a8b983a9f5fb3731c5a9434","tid":1631840,"uid":331388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce72e2c17174bb7d5b84e938c9a150a0fb850bb8","tid":1631840,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:25:14.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁快入嚟洗POST"},{"pid":"41ebad95741c934434ff5c81cab269aff8be7879","tid":1631840,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:25:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"a8a23b91b5851982ac670376ac4e51765daa80fa","tid":1631840,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:26:17.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"71636ccb407b2481f0e1314d09d99b4fb9882dee","tid":1631840,"uid":175806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7號晚係關鍵！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">要令黨鐵全線第二日停駛</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">港豬們好耐未三罷啦</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n香港人．<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反抗</span></span><br />\n香港人．三罷</span>"},{"pid":"216ba022963ea87efbc2f282bbc31f08149e2de1","tid":1631840,"uid":279091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"吊哂你哋D三毛係咁帶風向 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家回帶7月1日:佢哋(義士)唔走，我哋都唔會走！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/692795324506293?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F692795324506293%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=42146bcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/692795324506293?sfns=mo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n我哋點都唔會割 團結就是力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 反抗</span></span>"},{"pid":"4566dc280290c91cd47339bc1bdc151c1c1e9951","tid":1631840,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:04.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n態度好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ecb87f33ef998bbfc61eed4656460f8f4df363","tid":1631840,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:16.000Z","msg":"到底而家有幾多個洗POST手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c2d6172a74ecf899032a0db002262d59d54171","tid":1631840,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4566dc280290c91cd47339bc1bdc151c1c1e9951","tid":1631840,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:04.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n態度好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:18.000Z","msg":"。。。<br />\n其實個POST講得無錯<br />\n但兩個POST居然講啲嘢真係同一個公式咁<br />\n令我懷疑到底係咪真有其事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9170a1610f183f4d7d2538e2fee0ea956f8c3c6","tid":1631840,"uid":208118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:05.000Z","msg":"第二個poat係玩膠曲線屌原post"}]}